    data=s.recv(1024).decode()

        break
    print(data,end="")
    # parse equation like X * 15 = 65
    m=re.search(r'X\s*([+\-*/])\s*(-?\d+)\s*=\s*(-?\d+)', data)
    if not m:
        break
    op=m.group(1)
    a=int(m.group(2))
    b=int(m.group(3))
    # solve for X: X op a = b
    if op=='+':
        x=fractions.Fraction(b-a,1)
    elif op=='-':
        x=fractions.Fraction(b+a,1)
    elif op=='*':
        x=fractions.Fraction(b,a)
    elif op=='/':
        x=fractions.Fraction(b*a,1)
    else:
        break
    ans=str(x.numerator) if x.denominator==1 else f"{x.numerator}/{x.denominator}"
    s.sendall((ans+"\n").encode())
print(s.recv(4096).decode())
